          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The TVML frameworks provide several built-in ways to play media items. After loading the initial page, the app automatically plays music in the background. The user navigates between two images and the app loads and plays a video or audio media item after the user selects an image. Both of these media items play using the built-in TVMLJKit JS media player.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
